==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marsdenia
<hw>Mars*de"ni*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[NL.
From W. <ets>Marsden</ets>, an English author.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A genus of plants of the Milkweed family, mostly woody climbers
with fragrant flowers, several species of which furnish valuable fiber,
and one species (<spn>Marsdenia tinctoria</spn>) affords
indigo.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

